msgid ""
"<p>This module computes two-way frequencies for multiple response "
"questions, also known as \"Check All That Apply\" (CATA) questions.</p>\n"
"<p>Questions may be coded as:</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>several <strong>dummy (or indicator) variables</strong> using 0/1, 1/2, "
"Y/N for each possible answer;</li>\n"
"<li>a single <strong>multi-valued variable</strong> containing the checked "
"answers, separated by a symbol (usually \",\" or \";\").</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Credit "
"Cards</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>该模块计算多个题目的三歡题题和债到比例。</p>\n"
"<p>题目可以装作为。</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>多个 <strong>功机成式变量</strong> 使用 0/1, 1/2, Y/N 来设置每个可能的答案。</li>\n"
"<li>一个 <strong>多债式变量</strong> 包含选中的答案。</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>浏览文件可以在 Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Credit Cards 中找到。</p>"

