#: R/principal.b.R
#, fuzzy
msgid "PCA Standard Coordinates"
msgstr "PCA 标准坐标"

#: R/principal.b.R
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<p>This module computes <strong>Principal Component Analysis (PCA)</strong> "
"for several continuous variables. Computations are based on "
"<tt>stats::prcomp</tt> function.</p>\n"
"<p>Although rotated components are not principal components, they are "
"widely used. Only orthogonal rotations are available (from GPArotation "
"package).</p>\n"
"<p>Loadings (variable coordinates) and scores (observation coordinates) are "
"principal (scaled by the squareroot of eigenvalues).</p>\n"
"<p>Biplot follows \"Biplots in Practice\" (Michael Greenacre, 2010):</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li><strong>Form biplot:</strong> Scores are principal (scaled by "
"eigenvalues) while loadings are standard.</li>\n"
"<li><strong>Covariance biplot:</strong> Loadings are principal while scores "
"are standard. </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p><strong>Advanced options</strong>:</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li><strong>Standardize loadings:</strong> loadings are normalized with "
"sums of squared equal to 1 (instead of eigenvalues)</li>\n"
"<li><strong>Standardize scores:</strong> scores are normalized with "
"variances equal to 1 (instead of eigenvalues)</li>\n"
"<li><strong>Rotate eigenvectors:</strong> the rotation (varimax, etc) is "
"applied to eigenvectors (standard loadings) instead of principal loadings "
"(STATA way).</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>A sample file is included at Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Iris</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>该模块计算多个纯纯变量的 <strong>PCA</strong> 。计算为作于 <tt>stats::prcomp</tt> 函数。</p>\n"
"<p>该模块们能作。不能是主要延址。从 GPArotation 包作。</p>\n"
"<p>计算为作于 <tt>stats::prcomp</tt> 函数。</p>\n"
"<p>Biplot 以为 \"Biplots in Practice\" (Michael Greenacre, 2010)。</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li><strong>建竞 biplot、</strong> 计算为作于个空间和债到比例。</li>\n"
"<li><strong>都对比例 biplot、</strong> 计算为作于个空间和债到比例。</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p><strong>高级选项、</strong></p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li><strong>标准计算、</strong> 计算为作于个空间和债到比例。</li>\n"
"<li><strong>标准债到比例、</strong> 计算为作于个空间和债到比例。</li>\n"
"<li><strong>抽象债到比例、</strong> 计算为作于个空间和债到比例。</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>浏览文件可以在 Open > Data Library > vijPlots > Iris 中找到。</p>"

